# Tooling

stack: React 19, Vite, TypeScript strict, Tailwind v4
state: SQLite (local-first) via @sqlite.org/sqlite-wasm. no backend unless specified.
persistence: sqlite-wasm writes to OPFS (Origin Private File System). survives reload.
fallback: localStorage for ephemeral UI state (theme, sidebar open, etc.) only.
future: sync layer (e.g. ElectricSQL, cr-sqlite) if multi-device needed. don't abstract yet.
routing: React Router v7. no file-based routing.
